        "content": [
          {
            "text": "A five-minute tapping practice for the windfall fantasy, the recurring hope of a large, unexpected sum that will fix everything. The script does not shame the fantasy. It reads it as the signal it is: a message that something underneath needs attention. The practice works with that signal and moves toward the real, unglamorous wealth that consistent work produces.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "New to tapping? Read ",
